display_long_description:
Welcome to Juke Jungle: Project RE-RUN!

About Juke Jungle: Project RE-RUN

Juke Jungle is an exhilarating multiplayer game that takes the excitement of Gorilla Tag to new heights! With its adorable player models, diverse maps, and thrilling game modes, get ready to swing into action in this vibrant jungle-themed adventure!

### Game Features: Rising Lava, PVP coming soon, More gamemodes coming soon.

#### 1. Cute Player Models
Embrace the charm of our adorable player models! From playful monkeys to colorful creatures, enjoy exploring the jungle with these lovable characters.

#### 2. Diverse Maps
Explore a variety of intricately designed maps within the jungle setting. Each map offers its own challenges and surprises, keeping the gameplay fresh and exciting.

#### 3. Social Interaction
Engage with players from around the world! Form alliances, strategize with friends, and compete against others in this vibrant online community.

Enjoy!
